{"type": "article", "id": 8265, "title": "LEGO 积木包", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-09T07:30:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234628K8r5HLSEvoueVpI6.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tAgabag 是 Esty 上的一家店，它们专门为大家带了用 LEGO 积木做的各式各样的包，有手拿包，钱包，单肩包等等。这些包内部仍然是由普通的纺织材料构成，但是外部五颜六色的 LEGO 构成各式各样的图案，看上去个性十足。是不是让你想到了著名的三宅一生？这些包的价格在十几美元到几百美元不等，<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/agabag\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052346251zYrGliL74yPScZe.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234626FhLzZGkYuW4JAsP7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.78833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234626OJrCQ1bgW4ZRncmM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.87333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234627EXAiDsMe9tmd567u.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052346272rdc9Qs6Unq15mkH.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/upl